title: Farting: Why Vegans Quit Veganism (Indigestion & Ethics)
description: "You can't have an ethical movement that requires people to be flatulent 24 hours a day: do you want to be ethically right, or do you want to be farting all day?" The ex-vegan phenomenon has several recurring patterns: one is the ethical vegan who just can't make the diet work in terms of digestion, indigestion and flatulence.
